Paper: hep-th/9501034

Date: 1995-01-11

Title: Stochastic Variational Approach to Minimum Uncertainty States

Authors: F. Illuminati and L. Viola

Comments: 11 pages, latex, 12pt A4wide, no figures

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A28 (1995) 2953-2962

We introduce a new variational characterization of Gaussian diffusion processesas minimum uncertainty states. We then define a variational method constrainedby kinematics of diffusions and Schr\"{o}dinger dynamics to seek states oflocal minimum uncertainty for general non-harmonic potentials.